{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 83,
    "name": "سُورَةُ المُطَفِّفِينَ",
    "englishName": "Al-Mutaffifin",
    "englishNameTranslation": "Defrauding",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 36,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5849,
        "text": "Woe to those who give short measure,",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 587,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5850,
        "text": "who demand of other people full measure for themselves,",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 587,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5851,
        "text": "but when they give by measurement or weight to others, they give them less.",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 587,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5852,
        "text": "Do such people not realize that they will be raised up,",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 587,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5853,
        "text": "on a fateful Day.",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 587,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5854,
        "text": "The Day when mankind will stand before the Lord of the Universe?",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 587,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5855,
        "text": "Indeed! The record of the wicked is in the Sijjin --",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5856,
        "text": "and what could make you understand what the Sijjin is? --",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5857,
        "text": "it is a written record.",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5858,
        "text": "Woe, on that Day, to those who reject,",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5859,
        "text": "those who deny the Day of Judgement.",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5860,
        "text": "No one denies it except for the evil aggressor.",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5861,
        "text": "When Our revelations are conveyed to him, he says, \"Fables of the ancients!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5862,
        "text": "No! Their own deeds have cast a veil over their hearts.",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5863,
        "text": "Indeed! On that Day a barrier will be set between them and their Lord,",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5864,
        "text": "then they shall enter the Fire of Hell,",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5865,
        "text": "and they will be told, \"This is what you were wont to belie.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5866,
        "text": "But, the record of the righteous is [preserved] in the 'Illiyyin --",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5867,
        "text": "and what will make you understand what the 'Illiyyin is? --",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5868,
        "text": "a written record,",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5869,
        "text": "which those angels closest to God will bear witness to.",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5870,
        "text": "The virtuous will surely be in bliss,",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5871,
        "text": "seated on couches and gazing around in wonder.",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5872,
        "text": "You will find in their faces the brightness of bliss.",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5873,
        "text": "They will be given a drink of pure wine, sealed,",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5874,
        "text": "its seal will be of musk -- for this let the aspirants aspire --",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5875,
        "text": "a wine tempered with the waters of Tasnim,",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5876,
        "text": "a spring at which those drawn close to God will drink.",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5877,
        "text": "The wicked used to laugh at the believers --",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5878,
        "text": "when they passed by them, they would wink at one another;",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5879,
        "text": "and when they returned to their own people, they would speak of them jestingly;",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5880,
        "text": "and when they saw them, they said [scornfully], \"These men have surely gone astray,\"",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5881,
        "text": "though they were not sent to be their keepers --",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5882,
        "text": "so today those who believe shall [be able to] laugh at those who denied the truth",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 588,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5883,
        "text": "as they sit on couches, gazing around.",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 589,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5884,
        "text": "Have those who deny the truth [not] been paid back for their deeds?",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 589,
        "ruku": 525,
        "hizbQuarter": 235,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
      "identifier": "en.wahiduddin",
      "language": "en",
      "name": "Wahiduddin Khan",
      "englishName": "Wahiduddin Khan",
      "format": "text",
      "type": "translation",
      "direction": "ltr"
    }
  }
}